1
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:07,770
[A Prime Minister's Disguise]

2
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:10,330
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:11,350 --> 00:01:14,400
Kill! Kill! Kill!

4
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,230
Huo Jingheng!

5
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:18,560
Prime Minister Yue!

6
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,150
The cavalry you arranged to ambush my rear

7
00:01:21,150 --> 00:01:22,430
will not appear.

8
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,680
You're a genius at governing a country.

9
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,090
If it weren't for the incompetence
of the Emperor of Former Ning,

10
00:01:25,090 --> 00:01:27,400
[Huo Jingheng, Former Chief Commander
of the Volunteer Army]

11
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,640
you wouldn't have
ended up in this situation.

12
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,510
As long as you're willing to surrender,

13
00:01:31,510 --> 00:01:33,170
when I reorganize Ning State,

14
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:35,070
I'll still appoint you
as the Prime Minister.

15
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,090
The King of Ning was incompetent,

16
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:39,300
[Yue Chi, Prime Minister of Former Ning]

17
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:42,310
but I also have my reasons for
defending the land to the death.

18
00:01:42,310 --> 00:01:44,120
I, Yue Chi, can only fight...

19
00:01:45,509 --> 00:01:46,920
but not retreat!

20
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,640
Conquer the Dayan Pass!

21
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:07,290
Strike directly at the imperial capital!

22
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:16,030
♪ Bones were decaying in the sandstorm ♪

23
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:20,190
♪ The Dayan Pass witnessed numerous wars ♪

24
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:24,560
♪ General Yue guarded the pass alone
with a blade alone ♪

25
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,540
♪ To conquer this pass ♪

26
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:29,030
♪ 100,000 soldiers dared
not fight with him ♪

27
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:34,079
♪ But top talents tend to fight
with each other ♪

28
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:37,840
♪ The new ruler came up
with a clever strategy ♪

29
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:44,030
♪ After the defeat, General Yue's
anger couldn't cease ♪

30
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:48,150
♪ The emperor took power
and amended the rules ♪

31
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:50,590
♪ Thousands of people
sang and drank together ♪

32
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:52,310
♪ This peaceful time was the best ♪

33
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,440
Prime Minister Yue!

34
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:56,520
Don't let the soldiers die or get injured
unnecessarily anymore.

35
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,450
The Qilin Army only has dead people

36
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,590
and doesn't have surrendering soldiers.

37
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:02,190
I, Yue Chi, can only fight...

38
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,800
but not retreat!

39
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,190
Miss.

40
00:03:22,510 --> 00:03:24,390
The current Emperor is indeed good.

41
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:26,060
But if it weren't for
that battle two years ago,

42
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:28,260
where Yue Chi deliberately lost to him,

43
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:30,480
he might not have been able
to take control of Ning.

44
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,780
This song was composed
by a famous musician,

45
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:34,750
based on historical records and rumors.

46
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,840
I don't know why you're so certain that

47
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:39,560
Yue Chi deliberately
lost to the new Emperor.

48
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,310
The fall of the previous dynasty was
a matter of great importance.

49
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:43,840
Yue Chi wasn't stupid.

50
00:03:43,970 --> 00:03:45,910
He wouldn't go against the will of Heaven.

51
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,960
If the former Emperor had not

52
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,960
held Yue's family members hostage,

53
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:51,100
he wouldn't have gone to the battlefield.

54
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:53,230
How dare you speak so recklessly, sir?

55
00:03:53,290 --> 00:03:55,920
If Yue Chi had been forced
to go to the battlefield,

56
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:58,590
why would he deliberately seek defeat?

57
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,660
He wasn't seeking defeat.

58
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,050
Instead, he chose to die.

59
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:06,770
[Prince Anle's Mansion]

60
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:07,930
This Prince Anle's Mansion

61
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:09,870
is the home of Yue Chi, the guilty
official from the previous dynasty, right?

62
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:10,480
Yes.

63
00:04:10,580 --> 00:04:11,560
After Yue Chi's death,

64
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:14,010
His Majesty posthumously conferred
the title of Prince Anle on him.

65
00:04:14,010 --> 00:04:15,380
Though he's dead,

66
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:17,079
isn't his sister still alive?

67
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:17,420
I'm sure it's not something good.

68
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:20,880
[Imperial Decree]

69
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:24,000
According to Heaven's will,
the Emperor decrees that

70
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,390
Ms. Yue is virtuous, meticulous,

71
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,190
elegant and pure.

72
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:29,160
Therefore,

73
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,600
the title of Consort Yue will
be conferred on her.

74
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,480
[Yue Ling'er, Prince Anle's Younger Sister]

75
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,310
She shall enter the palace to
accompany the Emperor.

76
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:34,510
Respect it.

77
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:37,510
My Lady, what should we do now?

78
00:04:37,530 --> 00:04:38,730
If you enter the palace,

79
00:04:38,730 --> 00:04:40,540
how will you survive in there?

80
00:04:41,370 --> 00:04:42,290
My Lady.

81
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,330
Go to the Zuixiang Restaurant now.

82
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:47,720
Don't give up on yourself.

83
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:50,190
We need to stay calm right now.

84
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:52,300
Uncle,

85
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:54,640
I'm telling you to go find that person

86
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,080
to save my life.

87
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,460
The Emperor has issued a decree

88
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:57,830
[Dugu Xing, General of the Qilin Army]

89
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,690
to summon Lady Ling'er
to the palace as a consort.

90
00:04:59,690 --> 00:05:00,560
What?

91
00:05:04,710 --> 00:05:05,650
[Memorial Tablet of Yue Chi]

92
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,950
Ling'er.

93
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,660
Brother.

94
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,650
Brother!

95
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,700
You're finally back!

96
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:23,800
Alright.

97
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,560
How dare he think of marrying my sister?

98
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:28,450
Ling'er.

99
00:05:29,250 --> 00:05:30,560
Do you want me to kill him

100
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,420
or castrate him?

101
00:05:32,710 --> 00:05:33,650
No, no, no.

102
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:34,760
That's not necessary.

103
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,220
I won't let my sister

104
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,970
suffer such humiliation.

105
00:05:39,570 --> 00:05:41,480
Actually, it's not really humiliation.

106
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,990
I've heard that he's quite handsome,

107
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,550
and his figure is even...

108
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:50,120
But that's not the point.

109
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:52,290
The point is that in these two years
since you feigned death,

110
00:05:52,290 --> 00:05:54,390
he hasn't made things
difficult for our Yue family.

111
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:57,220
So, are you willing or not?

112
00:05:58,470 --> 00:05:59,980
Of course I'm not willing.

113
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,930
You have no idea.

114
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,930
The imperial palace is full of beauties,

115
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,570
and none of them are easy to deal with.

116
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:06,760
As your delicate little sister,

117
00:06:06,790 --> 00:06:08,740
I don't want to kneel under
the sun as my punishment.

118
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:11,010
Nor do I want to be pounced on
by cats or scared by dogs one day.

119
00:06:11,010 --> 00:06:12,110
And I definitely don't want to

120
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:14,080
be banished to a certain
mountain peak someday.

121
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,510
It's terrifying.

122
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:17,200
But...

123
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,670
But...

124
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:19,810
But...

125
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,240
Being a consort might not be a bad thing.

126
00:06:22,410 --> 00:06:24,860
It might bring me both glory and wealth

127
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,600
and also protect the Yue family.

128
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,600
Think about it.

129
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,480
What if

130
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,680
your sister really gains power one day?

131
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,820
Then you won't have to hide anymore.

132
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:34,440
What's more, our Yue family

133
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,580
won't be gossiped about anymore.

134
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,140
Why do I feel that

135
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,750
you're quite eager to marry him?

136
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:46,520
It's just because the imperial decree
has already been issued, isn't it?

137
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:49,460
What should I do after
entering the palace myself?

138
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:51,190
Alright.

139
00:06:51,409 --> 00:06:52,870
Let me think of a solution.

140
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:54,540
Think of...

141
00:06:54,670 --> 00:06:56,800
Think of a more proper solution.

142
00:07:36,370 --> 00:07:39,430
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

143
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,040
Your Majesty.

144
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,750
The Imperial Music Bureau has
choreographed a new dance.

145
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,159
Please enjoy it, Your Majesty.

146
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,030
Wei Zhang.

147
00:07:46,570 --> 00:07:48,370
There's been some improvement.

148
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,700
It looks like you haven't
been slacking off.

149
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:52,500
I strive to be diligent
in my duties, Your Majesty.

150
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:58,860
You come here.

151
00:07:58,860 --> 00:07:59,750
Wipe my sweat.

152
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:00,430
Yes.

153
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,950
If I had been really careless,

154
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,310
I might have been killed.

155
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:21,940
I wouldn't dare.

156
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,120
I'm not talking about you.

157
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,920
You don't have that ability.

158
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,320
I'm talking about her.

159
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:33,419
What do you mean by this, Your Majesty?

160
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,539
The trap of gentleness

161
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:37,350
is always fatal.

162
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,289
Tell me.

163
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,840
What do you want?

164
00:08:46,970 --> 00:08:47,850
Fine clothes?

165
00:08:48,940 --> 00:08:49,830
Jewelry?

166
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,210
A title?

167
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,740
Or is it my head that you want to get?

168
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,240
Treasonous usurper, I'll kill you!

169
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,640
Your Majesty, watch out!

170
00:09:36,330 --> 00:09:37,710
How did you discover it?

171
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:39,930
You seemed to be wiping my sweat.

172
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,480
Actually, you were checking my pulse.

173
00:09:43,830 --> 00:09:45,950
However, while you were examining me,

174
00:09:45,950 --> 00:09:47,670
I was also examining you.

175
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,430
I've underestimated you.

176
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:53,320
Too many people want to kill me.

177
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,140
I have to be cautious.

178
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:57,430
At least, you have some self-awareness.

179
00:09:57,470 --> 00:09:58,830
I may die today,

180
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:01,100
but there will be still
thousands of people like me.

181
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:01,870
You traitor!

182
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,420
In the netherworld,

183
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,760
I'll be waiting for you to die
with our dynasty's people!

184
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,660
Dying?

185
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,020
I haven't given you permission to die yet.

186
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:10,880
You're not going to die so easily.

187
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,690
Wei Zhang.

188
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,840
Keep a close eye on her.

189
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,900
Wait until I return
from the morning court.

190
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,750
You're going to enter the palace as me?

191
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:20,500
That's right.

192
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,240
Since childhood, people have
always said that we look alike.

193
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,660
I'll disguise myself properly

194
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,420
and explore the ways
for you in the palace.

195
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:27,720
Once I confirm that Huo Jingheng is
worthy of a lifelong commitment,

196
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,520
we'll switch our identities back
without anyone noticing.

197
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:29,790
Okay.

198
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:30,240
No way.

199
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,080
Commander,

200
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:32,320
you've fought against
the Emperor dozens of times

201
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,790
in dozens of battles.

202
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:35,120
What if he recognizes you?

203
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,340
That's impossible.

204
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,470
Back then, the army favored
a masculine appearance.

205
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:40,440
The former Emperor thought
I didn't look masculine enough,

206
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,440
so he ordered me to
wear a mask in the army.

207
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,150
Huo Jingheng has never seen my face.

208
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:46,960
But I've heard that
Huo Jingheng once studied

209
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,000
at the same school as you and your sister.

210
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,600
It only lasted for two years.

211
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:52,720
Back then, he was still a small kid.

212
00:11:14,020 --> 00:11:14,840
What's wrong?

213
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:16,800
Don't I look like my sister?

214
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:17,460
Well,

215
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:21,300
you just don't look feminine enough.

216
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:33,470
How am I not feminine enough?

217
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,940
Your waist isn't flexible enough,

218
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:39,240
and you're not petite enough.

219
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,790
I disagree.

220
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:42,230
At first glance,

221
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:44,500
he looks exactly like me.

222
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,330
That's right.

223
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:47,960
We're identical.

224
00:11:48,090 --> 00:11:49,750
Are you two really identical?

225
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,090
I know.

226
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,760
Brother,

227
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:55,440
apply some more rouge to your face.

228
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,140
And I have a mole
at the corner of my eye, don't I?

229
00:11:58,140 --> 00:12:00,470
If you add that,
we'll be exactly the same.

230
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:00,910
No need.

231
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:01,500
Just try it.

232
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,950
I don't think it's necessary.

233
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:04,280
I'm fine in this way now.

234
00:12:04,490 --> 00:12:06,090
Commander, please reconsider it.

235
00:12:06,090 --> 00:12:08,020
I know you care about Lady Ling'er.

236
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:12,030
But this plan is too unreliable.

237
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,300
It's not entirely for Ling'er.

238
00:12:18,300 --> 00:12:20,300
I do want to enter the palace myself.

239
00:12:20,450 --> 00:12:22,300
I heard that in this imperial examination,

240
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:24,970
many children of the officials from
the previous dynasty were selected.

241
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:27,140
I'm worried that he wants to
eliminate all threats

242
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:30,320
and settle scores with officials
from the previous dynasty.

243
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,630
What if Ling'er enters
the palace this time

244
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,040
and gets bullied?

245
00:12:34,930 --> 00:12:36,990
I can't let Ling'er suffer like that.

246
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:37,840
[Taiji Palace]

247
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,550
The Ministry of Revenue is
submitting a report.

248
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,960
This year, the weather in
all regions has been fine.

249
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,610
Our Ning Dynasty has been
established for two years.

250
00:12:43,610 --> 00:12:45,550
However, since the vassal states
paid the tributes and taxes,

251
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,720
vassal kings have become
the internal troubles of Ning.

252
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,410
But the external threats
are urgent problems.

253
00:12:49,410 --> 00:12:51,790
-Dispatch the army to the border.
-I suggest sending more soldiers there.

254
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:54,240
-The vassal kings might take advantage it.
-With both internal and external threats,

255
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,840
what should we do?

256
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,080
-Indeed.
-Indeed.

257
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,980
What should we do?

258
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,710
Since we can't make a decision,

259
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,670
let's adjourn the meeting.

260
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:06,430
Your Majesty, I have
one more matter to report.

261
00:13:06,740 --> 00:13:09,040
Although you wish to show
benevolence and righteousness,

262
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:11,830
the Yue family's daughter, Yue Ling'er,

263
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:15,180
is the younger sister of Yue Chi,
the former prime minister.

264
00:13:15,190 --> 00:13:17,940
Summoning her to the palace
as a consort is quite inappropriate.

265
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:19,680
This matter is of great importance.

266
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:21,740
Your Majesty, please reconsider it.

267
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:23,320
Yes, Your Majesty.

268
00:13:24,340 --> 00:13:26,470
