00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,540
He gets up earlier than the roosters

548
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:09,340
and goes to sleep later than the dogs.

549
00:26:09,340 --> 00:26:12,620
He's kind of a good emperor
who handles state affairs diligently.

550
00:26:12,620 --> 00:26:14,300
However, besides state affairs,

551
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:15,800
apart from practicing martial arts skills,

552
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:17,540
he only likes to collect weapons.

553
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:19,300
He has no other hobbies.

554
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:22,430
He hasn't summoned any consorts, either.

555
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:24,130
Could it be that...

556
00:26:24,130 --> 00:26:24,930
Your Majesty.

557
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:28,750
The Empress Dowager sent someone to ask
if you would go to the harem today.

558
00:26:28,750 --> 00:26:29,620
I won't.

559
00:26:29,970 --> 00:26:31,300
It's just as I expected.

560
00:26:31,500 --> 00:26:33,620
Does he have any unmentionable disease?

561
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:35,490
You won't go to see Consort Yue, either?

562
00:26:35,490 --> 00:26:36,210
No, I won't.

563
00:26:41,050 --> 00:26:42,960
Why are you staring at me like that?

564
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,680
Please forgive me first, Your Majesty.

565
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,460
Then I'll tell you.

566
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:45,920
Tell me.

567
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:47,790
Your Majesty.

568
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:50,070
You've been protective towards
Yue Ling'er for the past two years.

569
00:26:50,070 --> 00:26:51,890
Now that she has finally
entered the palace,

570
00:26:51,890 --> 00:26:53,110
why don't you...

571
00:26:53,790 --> 00:26:55,160
sing with her every night?

572
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:58,090
Instead, why are you only
reviewing documents here?

573
00:27:00,290 --> 00:27:02,730
That phrase is "partying every night."

574
00:27:03,050 --> 00:27:05,310
Only a doomed ruler would do such things.

575
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:07,630
I have no ulterior motives

576
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:10,270
towards Yue Ling'er.

577
00:27:10,510 --> 00:27:12,300
She's an orphan from the previous dynasty.

578
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:14,590
She has already lost
her brother's protection.

579
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:16,250
Anyone could bully her.

580
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,830
Her situation is not easy.

581
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:21,660
Though I've wanted to look after
the Yue family all these years,

582
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:25,190
I've been so busy with state affairs.

583
00:27:25,850 --> 00:27:28,670
It's better to bring her
into the palace directly.

584
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:30,990
At least, she'll be safe here.

585
00:27:40,930 --> 00:27:43,190
Huo Jingheng is too unscrupulous.

586
00:27:43,480 --> 00:27:45,160
What a bad idea he came up with.

587
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,480
His Majesty is unscrupulous?

588
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:48,160
His Majesty is the best Emperor.

589
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,530
Where did you come from?

590
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:50,450
Your Highness,

591
00:27:50,610 --> 00:27:53,320
I came to the imperial
capital as a refugee.

592
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,880
I was abducted by human traffickers.

593
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:56,880
His Majesty saved me while
having an incognito visit.

594
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,830
He even allowed me to enter
the palace and be a maid.

595
00:27:58,830 --> 00:28:00,760
He gave me a chance to make a living.

596
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:03,760
Actually, there are many things
that I can't do well.

597
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:05,790
But His Majesty never minds it.

598
00:28:05,790 --> 00:28:08,320
He even secretly asked
someone to protect me.

599
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,990
He doesn't want me to suffer.

600
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,400
His Majesty is a good person.

601
00:28:12,910 --> 00:28:15,110
Huo Jingheng may be a bit unscrupulous,

602
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:16,540
but he's not a bad person.

603
00:28:16,910 --> 00:28:18,830
He treats a young girl
he has never met before

604
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:20,880
with such kindness and righteousness.

605
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:23,340
He has done his best
to protect Ling'er, too.

606
00:28:23,690 --> 00:28:25,470
Perhaps for Ling'er,

607
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:28,080
he's really worthy of
a lifelong commitment.

608
00:28:28,500 --> 00:28:29,110
Yue,

609
00:28:29,330 --> 00:28:30,300
please get me a pen.

610
00:28:30,300 --> 00:28:32,480
I'm going to write a letter to my family.

611
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,030
Your Highness,

612
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:34,220
you don't need to send a letter.

613
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:35,600
I was just about to inform you that

614
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:37,060
your family had come here.

615
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:38,150
Who's here?

616
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,210
Over there.

617
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:43,930
Why are you here?

618
00:28:44,080 --> 00:28:45,490
What if someone discovers you?

619
00:28:45,490 --> 00:28:46,910
Brother, don't be nervous.

620
00:28:46,910 --> 00:28:48,170
Don't call me Brother.

621
00:28:50,090 --> 00:28:51,790
I came here in an aboveboard way.

622
00:28:51,790 --> 00:28:52,910
Don't worry.

623
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:55,540
I'm a maid from Prince Anle's Mansion.
Greetings, Consort Yue.

624
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:56,350
Do I look like a maid?

625
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:57,310
Of course not.

626
00:28:57,330 --> 00:28:58,080
Go back home now.

627
00:28:58,080 --> 00:28:59,010
This is not okay.

628
00:28:59,490 --> 00:29:00,740
You'd better go back
through the window.

629
00:29:00,740 --> 00:29:01,740
I don't want that.

630
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:02,660
Today,

631
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:03,910
I'm here to check your progress.

632
00:29:03,910 --> 00:29:04,800
How is it?

633
00:29:04,830 --> 00:29:06,470
How are you doing in the palace?

634
00:29:06,470 --> 00:29:08,800
Is Huo Jingheng a reliable man?

635
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:12,160
There's nothing particularly
special about him.

636
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:15,000
He just exercises every day,

637
00:29:15,020 --> 00:29:16,660
handles state affairs diligently
and has simple hobbies.

638
00:29:16,660 --> 00:29:17,400
He doesn't indulge in women's allure

639
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,200
and is quite healthy

640
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,130
with a good look.

641
00:29:19,130 --> 00:29:21,390
He also has the intention to protect you.

642
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:24,600
It seems that it's kind of
favorable for you.

643
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:29,450
So you're satisfied with Huo Jingheng?

644
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,830
That depends on what you think.

645
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,200
What do you think?

646
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,100
I...

647
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:34,130
Which of us

648
00:29:34,150 --> 00:29:35,120
is getting married?

649
00:29:35,120 --> 00:29:36,350
Aren't you my brother?

650
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:38,810
Shouldn't you vet him
for me more carefully?

651
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:41,790
Do you think Huo Jingheng
is reliable enough?

652
00:29:44,390 --> 00:29:47,390
He's relatively reliable.

653
00:29:48,290 --> 00:29:49,290
That's fine then.

654
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:53,590
But he's a very boring man.

655
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:54,720
As a husband,

656
00:29:55,050 --> 00:29:56,200
he might not be...

657
00:29:56,660 --> 00:29:57,640
That's not important.

658
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:59,110
As long as you're satisfied, it's fine.

659
00:29:59,110 --> 00:30:00,170
I'm satisfied?

660
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,460
So you're willing to enter the palace

661
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:06,010
and become the Empress?

662
00:30:06,020 --> 00:30:07,700
Yes, I am.

663
00:30:09,690 --> 00:30:10,590
Alright.

664
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,060
If that's the case,

665
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:15,040
I'll definitely help you
get the position of Empress.

666
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:17,360
I still need you to prepare
some things for me.

667
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:17,920
[Elegant Dwelling with Spring Grace]

668
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:19,980
Eunuch Gui, please stay for a moment.

669
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,170
Greetings, Your Highness.

670
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:26,690
I've heard that your mother has a cold

671
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,850
that remains unhealed for a long time.

672
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:30,190
I happen to have

673
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:31,850
a prescription from the Western Regions.

674
00:30:31,850 --> 00:30:33,510
It has miraculous effects for

675
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,700
treating cold illnesses.

676
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,390
Sister.

677
00:30:38,090 --> 00:30:39,090
It's Consort Yue.

678
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:41,640
She's trying to get close
to Eunuch Gui there.

679
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:43,110
Consort Yue, you're very thoughtful.

680
00:30:43,110 --> 00:30:46,210
I wonder what you want to order me to do.

681
00:30:46,850 --> 00:30:48,910
I wouldn't dare to give orders to you.

682
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:51,510
I just want you to do me a small favor.

683
00:30:52,130 --> 00:30:54,090
Then I'll leave now.

684
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,210
Over these years,

685
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:01,270
so many consorts have tried to
bribe people from the Yongqian Palace

686
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:02,350
to gain His Majesty's favor.

687
00:31:02,350 --> 00:31:04,830
Have you ever seen His Majesty
pay any attention to them?

688
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:07,300
She might irritate His Majesty

689
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:10,030
and be convicted of a serious crime.

690
00:31:18,060 --> 00:31:19,150
What is this?

691
00:31:21,110 --> 00:31:22,740
It's a gift from Consort Yue.

692
00:31:22,770 --> 00:31:25,240
I dare not to open it arbitrarily.

693
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:26,040
Consort Yue?

694
00:31:34,770 --> 00:31:36,440
Your Majesty, please spare my life!

695
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:38,090
I know nothing about it!

696
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:41,370
Let's go to the Fengluan Palace now.

697
00:31:43,320 --> 00:31:44,050
Consort Yue.

698
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:45,710
How dare you!

699
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:46,310
Guards!

700
00:31:46,330 --> 00:31:47,200
Arrest her!

701
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:51,800
How did you get this Qinggang Dagger?

702
00:31:56,350 --> 00:31:57,300
Is it genuine?

703
00:31:58,300 --> 00:32:00,300
Do you have any other ones like this?

704
00:32:00,330 --> 00:32:02,940
Your Majesty, why don't we go inside to talk?

705
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,160
Sister.

706
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:14,180
Sister, bad news.

707
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:17,170
I heard that His Majesty
went to the Fengluan Palace.

708
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,040
Why are you panicking?

709
00:32:19,170 --> 00:32:22,630
Perhaps His Majesty just
went inside for a brief visit.

710
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:25,960
Cao Pi, the Crown Prince of Wei,
made three powerful daggers.

711
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,470
One of them had patterns like ice

712
00:32:27,470 --> 00:32:28,800
and was named Qinggang.

713
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:31,460
My brother got it by chance
when he was alive.

714
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:32,940
Since it's destined to be with you,

715
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,540
then I'll give it to you.

716
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,310
Sister, bad news!

717
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:41,170
I heard that His Majesty
stayed there overnight.

718
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,570
Perhaps His Majesty was just
interested in her momentarily.

719
00:32:43,570 --> 00:32:45,230
He'll forget her in a few days.

720
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:47,540
This one is beautiful, too.

721
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:48,880
This battle-axe

722
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:50,130
is extremely sharp

723
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,630
and powerful.

724
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:55,260
The Panlong Rod.

725
00:32:55,410 --> 00:32:56,990
It is said to have originated
from Emperor Taizu of Song.

726
00:32:56,990 --> 00:32:58,390
As the saying goes, "Fists strike the centerline,

727
00:32:58,390 --> 00:32:59,600
while rods strike a whole area."

728
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,140
"When the Panlong Rod is used,

729
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:03,500
its power can break mountains and rivers."

730
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:04,600
Were these treasures

731
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:07,370
truly acquired by your brother
by chance when he was alive?

732
00:33:07,370 --> 00:33:09,510
My brother was used to seeing
rare treasures when he was alive.

733
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:11,040
These are just a few of them.

734
00:33:11,090 --> 00:33:11,750
Sister!

735
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:12,380
Bad news!

736
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,700
What is it now?

737
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:15,810
The news is spread in the entire harem.

738
00:33:15,810 --> 00:33:18,590
His Majesty has been staying at
Fengluan Palace for over 10 days in a row.

739
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:20,790
Consort Yue has become the favored one.

740
00:33:21,170 --> 00:33:22,640
Your Majesty, if you like them,

741
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:24,100
you can take them all away.

742
00:33:24,130 --> 00:33:25,020
Okay.

743
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:26,770
Consort Yue, you're generous.

744
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:28,470
I'm so pleased with you.

745
00:33:29,090 --> 00:33:31,190
These are all my treasures.

746
00:33:31,430 --> 00:33:32,920
I was just being polite.

747
00:33:32,950 --> 00:33:34,350
You really want them all?

748
00:33:37,990 --> 00:33:39,190
You may all leave now.

749
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:15,389
Father, Mother,

750
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:16,850
Eldest Brother and Second Brother.

751
00:34:16,850 --> 00:34:18,460
[Memorial Tablet of My Father, Qu Tengsheng]
[Memorial Tablet of My Mother, Zhang Huayu]

752
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,850
I'm here to see you all.

753
00:34:19,850 --> 00:34:21,440
[Memorial Tablet of My Brother, Qu Zhousheng]
[Memorial Tablet of My Brother, Qu Liusheng]

754
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,330
If Yue Chi had not

755
00:34:23,350 --> 00:34:25,460
set up a trap in Shilipo back then,

756
00:34:26,290 --> 00:34:29,690
my father and brothers wouldn't
have been killed in Shilipo.

757
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:33,440
And my mother wouldn't have died of grief.

758
00:34:33,659 --> 00:34:37,300
Our Qu family wouldn't have been ruined.

759
00:34:39,260 --> 00:34:40,480
Don't worry.

760
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:43,230
I'll make the Yue family
pay the price with their lives

761
00:34:43,230 --> 00:34:45,060
to comfort your souls in Heaven.

762
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:47,000
[Memorial Tablet of My Father, Qu Tengsheng]
[Memorial Tablet of My Mother, Zhang Huayu]

763
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:47,219
[Memorial Tablet of My Brother, Qu Zhousheng]
[Memorial Tablet of My Brother, Qu Liusheng]

764
00:34:47,219 --> 00:34:48,230
Yue Ling'er.

765
00:34:48,969 --> 00:34:51,500
As for all the crimes
your brother committed,

766
00:34:51,969 --> 00:34:55,650
I'll make you pay the price for them all.
